value.title: Learn Starcraft - Build Orders Vs Zerg (Terran, Zerg & Protoss Build Guide)
value.excerpt: A build as each race versus Zerg! These are general build guides, not exact textbook orders, because no plan survives contact with the enemy! Timestamps: 0:15 - Terran vs Zerg 11:00 - Protoss vs Zerg 24:00 - Zerg vs Zerg

value.title: Learn Starcraft - SPEEDRUN TO MASTERS RANDOM | 30 Wins, 0 Losses - Terran, Zerg & Protoss
value.excerpt: Making sure to use safe, solid builds to get an advantage when playing smart! Most build orders I think could be copied to success for platinum/diamond players. value.title: Learn Starcraft - Zerg v Protoss Build Order! (Updated 2018)
value.excerpt: A basic build to scout and react to a Protoss, and then overwhelm them with the swarm! Meant for lower level players looking for direction, not higher level looking for the dankest meta. -- Watch live at https://www.twitch.tv/wintergaming
